1. To target an individual service instance deployment, retrieve the GUID of your
service instance with the cf CLI command:

	```
	cf service MY-SERVICE --guid
	```

1. View VMs in the deployment by running the following command:

	```
	bosh -d DEPLOYMENT-NAME instances
	```

1. SSH onto a VM by running the following command:

	```
	bosh -d service-instance_GUID ssh
	```

1. Download the instance logs by running the following command:

	```
	bosh -d service-instance_GUID logs
	```
